00:55:09.580 --> 00:55:13.350
going on, or it's a team that's just kind of starting to develop an idea, and

953
00:55:13.360 --> 00:55:15.160
they're not sure which direction they want to go yet.

954
00:55:15.940 --> 00:55:19.400
So we can bring together a group of advocates to give feedback

955
00:55:19.920 --> 00:55:22.640
during a focus session with an investigator.

956
00:55:22.700 --> 00:55:23.860
So that's another thing we're going to be doing.

957
00:55:24.120 --> 00:55:27.820
So we do pay, of course, the advocates for their time, $50

958
00:55:28.180 --> 00:55:31.500
per hour. And so the research

