00:55:35.200 --> 00:55:39.180
And if they come into in-person meetings, they have to pay for

961
00:55:39.200 --> 00:55:42.499
their mileage and other travel expenses if they stay overnight.

962
00:55:43.040 --> 00:55:46.700
So I'm going to give just two examples of projects that have worked with us, with

